Abjuration
Level: Druid 4, Ranger 3
Components: V,S
Range: Personal
Target: You
Duration: 24 hours

This spell calls upon the primal forces of creation to grant you the senses of your primitive ancestors. You gain low-light vision and a +5 bonus on Listen and Spot checks.

<i>Translucent, catlike eyes appear over your own, flaring brightly for a moment before fading to invisibility.</i>